## Server-Client system for running multiple VPS instances
![Pasted image 20220509224120.png](data:image/png;base64,)

Ubuntu server application and Windows Server client application, providing monitoring of multiple VPS with automated bot software running on them:
- Collecting data from VPSs for monitoring with Airtable base
- Sending commands to VPSs direct from Airtable
- Receiving reports from bot apps on VPSs and saving them to Airtable base
